snippet.title: Among Us VR - Gameplay Trailer 💫 omggggg omg omg omg omg omg
snippet.description:
Among Us VR is a game of teamwork and betrayal for 4-10 players...in space! Grab your headset and get ready. Crewmates work together to complete tasks before one or more Impostors can kill everyone aboard. All of the same betrayal and deceit as the original game, but now in a virtual Skeld.

Coming Holiday 2022. Revealed as part of the Meta Quest Gaming Showcase.

More info:
➫ Among Us VR on Twitter: https://twitter.com/AmongUsVR
➫ Among Us VR Website: https://www.innersloth.com/games/among-us-vr/
